<left><b>T'Kagi Ro Officer</left><br>

<left><b>The Pride of Halas</b></left><br>

<left><i>"I should be able to use gnomes as one handed blunt weapons!!"</i></left></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Tarsiger</span><br> <b>is too scared to Register</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/17/00 1:51:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Archery</span><hr size=1> Bah!  Ya squak like a paladin about nonsense.  Effectiveness is what ya should be askin yerself about. Is my bow an effective addition to my weapons arsenal?  By the Blood of the Tribunal yer damn right it is!  It allows me to effectively and selectively engage the enemy....while limiting the risks to me and my group.  A warrior must use his brain in a battle also, lest they end up splattered in the snow.  Effectiveness is the only concern.....honor?  Bah!  If yer blade is bloody and yer standing at the end it was a honorable battle.<br>
<br>
Cayce MacMurray<br>
Warrior of 32 Winters<br>
Current Ravager of Kaesora<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujaikarhalfelf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaikar HalfElf</A></span><br> <b>Everybody's Favorite Hero</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/17/00 2:12:04 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.feir-dal.net/jaikarphoto.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> Archery?! Whut...ye sum kinda tree-hugger? Next thing ye know, ye'll wanna start smellin' animal dung and lookin' fer berries...<br>
<br>
Personally, I like the feel o' cold steel in me hand -- I use shuriken. If it's made o' wood...consider it fire kindlin'. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Krugor</span><br> <b>is too scared to Register</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/17/00 2:44:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> I all ways try to open with my bow.  It may just hit for a little damage but remember 1 point of damage can mean the difference between victory and death.  So I would always use a bow its a great way to pull and if your good you can get 2 or 3 shots off be for your foe gets to you.  <br>
<br>
Krugor <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utorqdacraknek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Torq da Craknek</A></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/17/00 2:49:16 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> Me uses arrows all da time for gettin da beasty's attenshun. Me not very gud at usin da bow, but it no matter. Dat cuz if me hit dem or not, dey com a runnin just from me shootin at em. Sumtimz me hit dem real gud wit crit, dat really tik dem off.<br>
<br>
Me tried dem lil shurken tingies, but me keep forgettin not to put in back pocket wen me sits down so me trew dem away. Me still pickin lil pieces o' metal outta me arse after dat one.<br>
<br>
Torq da Craknek<br>
Ogre Warrior<br>
Seventh Hammer<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utubolard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tubolard</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/17/00 10:30:51 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.skorchers.com/revive/members/pics/tubolard60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> bow an arrow am gudd fer pullin so yu no git hacked on while returnin ta yur grup. it also necesity in plain raids iffin yu pikin dem off thu  fdethed/monk puller.<br>
<br>
<br>
