  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uadexxeda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adex Xeda</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://acs.tamu.edu/~dwr9806/adex_icon.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/18/00 11:08:34 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://acs.tamu.edu/~dwr9806/adex_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> <br>
A 150 range bow will give you a few seconds lead time when pulling a mob back to your camp before they hit on you on the way back. That saves HP, and in the long run saves mana which saves downtime. Bows are good for pulling.<br>
<br>
Also,  Its a skill, as a warrior we should use all our skills to our advantange. Don't buy that paladin line about bows being for wimps or something. Warriors do whatever it takes to get the job done. <br>
<br>
Also I it gives me no greater joy than to crit hit with my bow and make the nearby ranger jealous.<br>
<br>
Also, Its fun as hell to use after get a high damage bow and a high skill. <p>Adex Xeda "Veeshan"<BR>
52 Warrior and Toy of the Rainmaker <BR>
"You can't hit what you can't touch." <BR>
<IMG SRC= http://acs.tamu.edu/~dwr9806/adex_vs_nag1.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujaramena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaramena</A></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/18/00 12:19:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> Get the best bow you can find, and start making arrows to fill it.  there are some good sights out there - one about the &quot;cheapest way to fletch&quot;.  by doing this, my fletching skill is now very good, never really sold my arrows, just made them for myself and handed out to group members if they were low.  Always chuckled at the look of surprise on the other warrior's faces when they found they could pull the beastie from so much farther away (those long range arrows are GREAT).  Just from handing out bows, several of my warrior friends are now trying to catch up in fletching skill, hehe.<br>
<br>
so definately, allows you to show even more of the warriors superiority in anything we try to do.<br>
<br>
Jaramena Tankette<br>
Barbarian Warrior of the 31 season<br>
Nameless<br>
Officer of The First Seals <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> warrior of kelethin</span><br> <b>is too scared to Register</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/19/00 4:18:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   bow and arrows kick ass</span><hr size=1> arechery is one of the best skills for a warrior i can hit with my bow for around 27 points at 18 and very very fast. fleacthing is so great too cause u have tons of kickass arrows u can make. its way better then shurikans . they have alot more range and very good damge. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukhaba.showPublicProfile?language=EN>khaba</A></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/20/00 11:10:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: bow and arrows kick ass</span><hr size=1> Da' bow is gud, but get da sow magic and a weighted axe is better...smack 'em to kingdom come...run...get ur choppas or smacka...go aggro and don't let 'em mobs taunt ya off yer target.<br>
For dem uber mobs use yer fattest recurve bow.<br>
Big blak troll bows are killas...dig dat...but know when to use da big puller axe.<br>
Khaba Khaan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ustoli.showPublicProfile?language=EN>stoli</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.nietoservices.com/citrix/stoli11.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>   <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/00 6:28:59 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.nietoservices.com/citrix/stoli11.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I archery useful for warriors?</span><hr size=1> <br>
